@startuml
title 合同生命周期状态图

[*] --> Draft : 创建合同
Draft --> Executing : StartExecution()
Draft --> Cancelled : Cancel(reason)
Draft --> Terminated : 不允许

Executing --> Completed : Complete() / 全部回款计划 Paid
Executing --> Cancelled : Cancel(reason)
Executing --> Terminated : Terminate(reason)

Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]
Terminated --> [*]

note right of Draft
Draft 可编辑基础信息、
合同明细和回款计划。
end note

note right of Cancelled
作废必须填写原因；
已作废合同不能登记回款。
end note

@enduml
